==============================================================================

In Kubernetes, Service types are abstractions that define how to expose Pods. The common types are:

      ClusterIP (default)
      
      NodePort
      
      LoadBalancer

-------------------------------------------

flow :

                   Client (Internet)
                      ↓
                   External Load Balancer
                      ↓
                   NodePort (on a Kubernetes Node)
                      ↓
                   ClusterIP (Kubernetes internal)
                      ↓
                   Pod (endpoint)


